<%= content_for :title, t('.title') %>

<div class="page-sub-navigation show-for-large" data-sticky-container>
  <div class="sticky" data-sticky data-anchor="legal" data-active-class>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="columns text-right">
        <nav data-magellan>
          <ul class="horizontal menu">
            <li><%= link_to yield(:title), '#about' %></li>
            <li><%= link_to t('.news'), '#news' %></li>
            <li><%= link_to t('.downloads'), '#downloads' %></li>
            <li><%= link_to t('.careers'), '#careers' %></li>
            <li><%= link_to t('.legal'), '#aboutlegal' %></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="hide-for-large">
  <div class="page-sub-bottom-nav">
    <nav data-magellan>
      <ul class="menu icon-top expanded">
        <li><%= link_to yield(:title), '#about' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to t('.news'), '#news' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to t('.downloads'), '#downloads' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to t('.careers'), '#careers' %></li>
        <li><%= link_to t('.legal'), '#legal' %></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="medium-10 medium-centered large-12 columns about-us-sections">

  <section class="row" id="about" data-magellan-target="about">
    <div class="small-12 columns">
      <h1><%= yield :title %></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="large-7 columns">
      <div class="flex-video">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OE9_JYiA7zc" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="small-10 small-pull-1 small-push-1 large-push-0 large-pull-0 large-5 columns">
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Etiam mattis erat non ipsum scelerisque interdum. Fusce malesuada purus massa, consectetur luctus est condimentum eget. Nullam eu porttitor sapien, in euismod est. In vel sem vehicula ex elementum mattis eget vel sapien. Nullam in rutrum ante. Vivamus rhoncus dignissim eros, ac feugiat quam tempor sit amet. Vestibulum ullamcorper feugiat massa id pellentesque. Integer nisi mi, laoreet id tellus ac, condimentum blandit lacus. Mauris non augue malesuada, commodo ex eget, facilisis lectus. Duis sem mi, finibus id lacus non, vulputate euismod risus.</p>
      <p>Quisque eleifend elementum leo sit amet mattis. Donec mollis euismod gravida. Aenean ut posuere velit. Vivamus consectetur eu justo hendrerit laoreet. Nunc felis urna, finibus a ante mattis, malesuada luctus turpis. Proin porta non augue ut tristique. Donec eget tempor lacus. Nulla pharetra bibendum nisi eu vulputate. Mauris blandit diam nec metus feugiat ultrices.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="news" data-magellan-target="news">
    <div class="row columns">
      <h1><%= t '.news' %></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="row news-articles-container">
      <div class="news-article">
        <%= link_to @featured_article do %>
          <%= attachment_image_tag @featured_article, :hero_image, :fill, 816, 459, fallback: 'http://placehold.it/816x459' %>
          <h2><%= @featured_article.title %></h2>
          <p><%= @featured_article.subtitle %></p>
        <% end if @featured_article %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="large-7 columns news-article-blurbs">

        <%= render partial: 'recent_article', collection: @recent_articles %>

        <%= content_tag :div, class: 'read-more' do %>
          <%= link_to news_path, class: "goto-new" do %>
            <%= t(".more_stories") %>
          <% end %>
        <% end if Article.count > 4 %>
      </div>
      <div class="large-5 columns news-article-list show-for-large">
        <ul class="tabs" data-tabs id="news-article-tabs">
          <li class="tabs-title is-active"><a href="#news-toparticles" aria-selected="true"><h5><%= t('.top_articles') %></h5></a></li>
          <li class="tabs-title"><a href="#news-topics"><h5><%= t('.topics') %></h5></a></li>
          <li class="tabs-title"><a href="#news-regions"><h5><%= t('.regions') %></h5></a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tabs-content" data-tabs-content="news-article-tabs">
          <div class="tabs-panel is-active news-toparticles" id="news-toparticles">
            <ol>
              <%= render partial: 'top_article', collection: @top_articles %>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <div class="tabs-panel" id="news-topics">
            <ol>
              <%= render partial: 'top_tag', collection: @top_tags %>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <div class="tabs-panel" id="news-regions">
            <ul>
              <%= render partial: 'continent', collection: CONTINENTS %>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="row about-media" id="downloads" data-magellan-target="downloads">
    <div class="small-12 columns">
      <h1>Media Library</h1>
    </div>

    <%= render partial: 'media_download', collection: @media_downloads %>

    <!-- if more than 6 media available -->
    <%= content_tag :div, class: 'read-more small-12 columns' do %>
      <a href="#" class="expand-container"><%= t('.more_media') %></a>
    <% end if MediaDownload.count > 6 %>
  </section>

  </div>
</div>

<section class="about-careers-container" id="careers" data-magellan-target="careers">
  <h1><%= t(".careers") %></h1>
  <%= link_to t('.find_career'), 'http://wavetronix.recruiterbox.com', class: 'button rounded large', target: '_blank' %>
</section>

<section class="about-legal-container" id="aboutlegal" data-magellan-target="legal">
  <h1><%= t(".legal") %></h1>
  <!-- <button class="button rounded large"><%= t('.view_legal') %></button> -->
  <%= link_to t('.view_legal'), legal_path, class: 'button rounded large' %>
</section>
